根据SPEI指数，使用2000年1月至2022年12月的逐月统计数据（包括月均2: According to the SPEI index, monthly statistical data from January 2000 to December 2022, including monthly average 2-meter temperature and monthly total precipitation data, were used for calculation.

空间范围默认为中国区域，范围为：经度113.01494046724021°~ 1: The spatial range defaults to the Chinese region, ranging from longitude 113.01494046724021 ° to 113.9181165740333 °, latitude 30.07345722586285 ° to 30.9597805438586 °.
时间范围默认为2018年7月1日至2018年12月1日。: The default time range is from July 1, 2018 to December 1, 2018.

根据NDBI指数，使用“LC08_L1TP_ARD_EO”数据（分析就绪型Lan: According to the NDBI index, calculate using the "LC08_L1TP_ARD-EO" data (analyzing ready Landsat8 data).
使用深度学习模型OSNet_ConvNeXt-N_OSDataset_69，以及: Using the Deep Learning Model OSNet_ConvNeXt N_OSDataset_69, and OPT in the WHU-OPT-SAR dataset_CorrectTif and SAR_CorrectTIF for change detection

Use images from different periods to extract water bodies and calculate the frequency of their occurrence. The higher the frequency of water body appearance, the darker the color.
